						<div class="postbody">I've got this rom for the PC-Engine that is a port of Super Mario Bros. Does anybody know the history on this? It seems to also be found in a 6-in-1 fami collection.  
<br />
<br />Did they use the original code from the famicom game, or is this programmed from the ground up? Because except for the colors and sound being a little off, it's indistinguishable from the original to me.</div>

