						<div class="postbody">You could try comparing the ROMs and see if you find any chunks of code that are the same in both of them. Anything that accesses  the APU, PPU or joypads would've had to be partially or completely rewritten, but the main game "engine" should've been possible to move from the NES to the PCE with few changes.</div>

