					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">NES games can be hacked (with considerable effort) to run on the PCE.
<br />
<br />Those NES hacks are from Image, a Finnish cracking group. Since Image were Finnish, they used the PAL ROM of Super Mario Bros. for their PCE conversion, thus the colours are a bit off and the speed is wrong on NTSC systems such as the PCE/Turbo.  Image also hid a few pictures at the end (?) of their PCE ROMs; go have a look for them in some tile editors.</div>

					
